d.network.cz/\">Bird</a> - The BIRD project aims to develop a fully functional dynamic IP routing daemon primarily targeted on (but not limited to) Linux, FreeBSD and other UNIX-like systems and distributed under the GNU General Public License.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-10-20T07:55:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"sdnds-tw/awesome-sdn","categoryHTML":"<h1>Router</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/osrg/gobgp\">gobgp</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/osrg/gobgp\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2.2k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2198,\"repo\":\"osrg/gobgp\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - GoBGP is an open source BGP implementation designed from scratch for modern environment and implemented in a modern programming language, the Go Programming Language.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-10-20T07:55:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"sdnds-tw/awesome-sdn","categoryHTML":"<h1>Router</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartbgp/yabgp\">yabgp</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartbgp/yabgp\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4p